Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.37,0:37:45.20,Default,,0,0,0008,,{\an8\blur3}罗斯威尔 市区范围 高空3570
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.58,0:40:36.08,Default,,0,0,0008,,{\an8\blur3}人工智能实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上溯至宇宙初始 周遭还只是一片漆黑{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知何时 忽地一声巨响{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then... Bang!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}时间空间以及物质皆由此发端{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Giving birth to an endless expanding existence{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此后不断膨胀 延伸 永无止境{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一天 新的发现都在不断为我们解开{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕴藏于这里的那些神秘莫测{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the mysterious, the mind-blowing,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}令人大开眼界 致命的秘密{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the deadly secrets of a place we call{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们称这个地方为"宇宙"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成千上万的人声称亲眼见过不明飞行物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Thousands of witnesses have claimed to see UFOs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们对此现象的描述是惊人的相似{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And their accounts are often strikingly similar.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坠落的飞盘 加上尸体残骸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You have a crashed saucer, but also some crashed bodies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有政府介入的掩饰行为{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You have government cover-up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主流科学一致认为目前证据不足{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Mainstream science says the evidence just isn't there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从不明飞行物到外星飞船是一个很大的跨越{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's a big jump between a UFO and an extraterrestrial spacecraft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但如果不明飞行物的确是外星飞船{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But if UFOs were really extraterrestrial craft,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那其中又隐藏了何种令人匪夷所思的技术{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}what kind of mind-bending technologies would we find under the hood?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外星飞船一定要有特殊技术{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You'd have to have some sort of technology that was capable{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才能抵消惯性作用{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of canceling the effects of inertia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不明飞行物神秘面纱后的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When it comes to Unidentified Flying Objects,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真实面目究竟是什么呢{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}what is the real deal?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对于无数追随者来说{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}For millions of believers,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一切始于1947年6月24日{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it all began on June 24, 1947.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}商人飞行员肯尼斯·阿诺德当时正在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A businessman and pilot named Kenneth Arnold is flying solo{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}华盛顿州的雷尼尔山附近独自飞行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}near Mount Rainier, Washington.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然 他看到九个飞行器组成一队{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Suddenly he sees a group of nine aircraft{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以惊人的速度飞行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}moving at incredible speeds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些飞行器高度反光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They were highly reflective,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并以超音速列队飞行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and they were flying at supersonic speeds,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它们还会突然改变航线{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in formation, changing course abruptly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以当时的技术无法达到该速度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The speeds were unattainable at the time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时喷气式飞机和超音速飞机还未问世{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This was before the age of jets and certainly supersonic jets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身为训练有素的飞行员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Being a trained pilot,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了确认自己看到的是飞行器{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}he did several things to corroborate their existence{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.79,0:02:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而不是某种大气效应{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to make sure he wasn't seeing some kind of atmospheric effect.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他摆动自己的头 改变机身的角度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}He changed his... his head angle. He changed the aircraft angle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他甚至调整了飞机位置{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}He even positioned the aircraft such that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让白雪作为这群飞行器的背景{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}there was a light snow in the background behind the objects,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而在白雪的映衬下 这群飞行器显得很暗{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and they appeared dark against a light surface.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但就在阿诺德设法接近时 不明物体消失了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Before Arnold can maneuver closer, the objects are gone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这算得上是现代史无前例的发现{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It was basically unprecedented in modern times.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从未有人见过类似的物体{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No one had seen anything like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}后来在他讲述事件时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the days that follow, newspaper reporters misquote Arnold,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记者误引了阿诺德的话{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as he tries to make sense of the incident.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当时他说它的飞行方式像碟子在水上漂{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In fact, he said it moved like saucers skipping on water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而记者把这个意思理解错了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, of course, the reporter kind of messed that up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而报道说它们看起来像碟子{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in reporting it and said that they looked like saucers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"飞碟"一词由此而生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The term "Flying saucer" is born.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿诺德的发现首开现代不明飞行物现象的先河{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And Arnold's encounter launches the modern UFO phenomenon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:03:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几周后 即在1947年的夏天{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Weeks later, in the summer of 1947,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在新墨西哥州的罗斯威尔附近发生了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}perhaps the most famous incident involving an Unidentified Flying Object{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}史上最著名的不明飞行物事件{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is reported near Roswell, New Mexico.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}罗斯威尔事件是典型的不明飞行物现象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Roswell's become the poster child of the UFO phenomenon,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因其具备所有必要因素{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because it has all the necessary ingredients.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坠落的飞碟 加上尸体残骸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You have a crashed saucer, but also some crashed bodies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有政府介入 他们绝对隐瞒了实情{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You have government cover-up. There was some sort of cover-up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当局发布的是虚假信息{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There was misinformation given out by the authorities.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}消息最初是从空军那边传出的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The original account put out by the air force at the time was{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说这就是来自外太空的飞碟{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that this was a flying saucer of alien origin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但没过多久 这个说法就被否认了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then later, very quickly, was denied, and the story then{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改称这是个坠毁的气象气球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}was that this was a weather balloon which had crashed and{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上面没有载人{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that there were no occupants on board{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说有外星人更是无稽之谈{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and that there was nothing extraterrestrial about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他目击者宣称看到了坠毁飞行器的残片{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Other witnesses claimed to have seen actual pieces of a crashed spacecraft...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报道称 这些材料超越了当时的科技水平{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Materials that are reportedly unknown to science.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿诺德的目击与罗斯威尔事件{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Both Arnold's sighting and the Roswell incident remain{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都未得到官方证实 二者本身也颇有争议{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}officially unconfirmed and highly controversial.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几乎每年都有许多关于不明物体的报道{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Just about every year, there are thousands of reported sightings{\r}
